{
  "stem": "14552.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- in the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three tiers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bunkbeds.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bunkbeds.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the boards were not meeting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a separation, so there was even more uncomfortable, because you hit the board, the edge of the board.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No mattress.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On slats, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the roof was leaking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now we had the-- when it was leaking, we couldn't move to the side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to get off the bunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then eventually, in those-- we had-- I had a sweater, some kind of a raggedy sweater.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually, the clothes got lice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was chlor powder, chlorine powder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would take that chlorine powder and wash myself with cold water, because I was-- I always worried about dirt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was-- it was cold water and that awfully smelling chlorine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were-- we had no hair, so it didn't get into our heads.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It didn't get into our-- we had no hair on our body, but it was on the clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the bedbugs formed in the wood from the dampness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that fell on us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were given the mid-day-- we were given a meal when it was raining and they didn't give the food outside and they kept us in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to stay in those bunks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They would hand us in a dish with the food, which-- with soup I never ate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I only ate the bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the food, the bugs were falling into that plate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I-- I said, I'd rather die than eat this, because the-- the utensils they used were bedpans, whatever happened to come.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If it was a bed pan, that's what they gave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if it was a regular pot or whatever, that they did not worry about.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
